{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2014/02/happy-in-dachu/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/entertainment/","name":"生活娱乐活动"}],"tags":[{"name":"DIY","path":"/tag/diy/"},{"name":"同事","path":"/tag/workmate/"},{"name":"圣诞节","path":"/tag/christmas/"},{"name":"大楚网","path":"/tag/dachu/"},{"name":"姜饼","path":"/tag/gingerbread/"},{"name":"年会","path":"/tag/annual-meeting/"},{"name":"武汉","path":"/tag/wuhan/"},{"name":"活动","path":"/tag/event/"},{"name":"腾讯","path":"/tag/tencent/"},{"name":"舞蹈","path":"/tag/dance/"},{"name":"魏梦瑶","path":"/tag/mengyao/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/cover21.jpg"},"path":"/2014/02/happy-in-dachu/","date":"2014-02-08T10:49:21.000Z","excerpt":"俺最近每天给别人更新新闻，却很久没有“更新自己”。以为明天又要上班，但刚才一看，明儿俺休息！突然得到了一个本来 … ","title":"圣诞姜饼DIY、年会开场舞-腾讯大楚网Q哥Q妹们真靓","content":"<p>俺最近每天给别人更新新闻，却很久没有“更新自己”。以为明天又要上班，但刚才一看，明儿俺休息！突然得到了一个本来就属于我的休息日，遂心情大好，抓紧时间来此更新。</p>\n<p>2013年底到武汉，在腾讯大楚网开始新的工作，离开宜昌三峡晚报、凯能数码、同学、老朋友，放下很多有趣的想法没有实现，但结识一批新朋友，并发现另外的精彩后，也算弥补了一些遗憾。当然不会忘了老朋友地！周末2天回宜昌参加凯能数码的年会，真是一趟说走就走的旅行！你们还记得我，很感动！</p>\n<p>还是这儿好，不怕写错别字，不怕更新不及时，不怕有错链，不怕要审核，随便意识流，我的地盘我做主。好！开始更新我自己的旧闻！</p>\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjY0NTczMzAw/v.swf\"/><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\"/><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\"/><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"/><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjY0NTczMzAw/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" quality=\"high\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"/></object></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dFHowm4u77k\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">到YouTube上观看</a></p>\n<p>2014-01-15，有情我的女神推开这台好戏的大门！在2014年腾讯武汉年会上，大楚网帅哥美女们欢乐上演开场舞。每个人都表现的很棒，最要感谢的是梦瑶的编舞和耐心教学。我能够参与其中倍感happy。舞台上短短几分钟的表演后，微信“舞班子”里顿时感慨万千，我们又兴奋又失落，我们这个小队伍何时又在一起呢？2014年我们要创造更多精彩！</p>\n<p><object width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjUyNTkzMDMy/v.swf\"/><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\"/><param name=\"quality\" value=\"high\"/><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\"/><embed width=\"480\" height=\"400\" align=\"middle\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNjUyNTkzMDMy/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" quality=\"high\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"/></object></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qZVFxF93Mvg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">到YouTube上观看</a></p>\n<p>2013-12-24，圣诞节前夕，腾讯大楚网湖北的同事们DIY姜饼屋，以为去可以饱餐一顿，可是从头整到尾也没尝一口姜饼什么味儿，凑个热闹还是比较好玩，这样的圣诞节很新颖！<br />\nMerry Christmas In WuHan DaChu<br />\nBGM:Upon A Christmas Night by Micheal Learns To Rock</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2014/02/happy-in-dachu/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}